
## Project Overview

Backend sudah dibangun menggunakan:

* Laravel 13
* REST API
* MySQL
* Image Optimization
* Dynamic Product System

---

# Current Backend Features

Backend yang sudah tersedia:

## Authentication Admin

* Login admin
* Dashboard admin
* CRUD system

---

## Category System

Admin dapat:

* tambah category
* edit category
* delete category
* aktif/nonaktif category

API category sudah siap digunakan.

---

## Product System

Admin dapat:

* tambah product
* edit product
* delete product
* upload thumbnail
* toggle active/inactive
* best seller toggle

Setiap product memiliki:

* category
* provider
* type
* billing_type
* code
* variants
* prices

---

## Product Variant System

Setiap product dapat memiliki:

* banyak variant
* banyak harga
* banyak purchase period

Contoh:

Softbank →

* 20GB
* 50GB
* Unlimited

---

## Purchase Period System

Digunakan untuk:

* bulanan
* 3 bulan
* 6 bulan
* 12 bulan

---

## Variant Price System

Digunakan untuk:

* harga tiap variant
* harga tiap periode

Contoh:

50GB:

* Monthly → ¥3000
* 6 Months → ¥15000

---

## Promo System

Admin dapat:

* tambah promo
* upload banner
* jadwalkan promo
* promo auto expired

Promo memiliki:

* title
* description
* image
* link
* start_date
* end_date

---

## Homepage API

Backend sudah menyediakan:

```bash
/api/home
```

Return:

* promos
* best sellers
* new products
* categories

Frontend homepage cukup 1 fetch.

---

## Product API

### Product List

```bash
/api/products
```

---

### Product Detail

```bash
/api/products/{slug}
```

---

## Search + Filter API

Backend support:

### Search

```bash
/api/products?search=softbank
```

---

### Filter by Category

```bash
/api/products?category=esim
```

---

### Filter by Type

```bash
/api/products?type=esim
```

---

### Filter by Billing

```bash
/api/products?billing=monthly
```

---

### Filter by Provider

```bash
/api/products?provider=docomo
```

---

### Combined Filter

```bash
/api/products?type=esim&billing=monthly
```

---

# Dynamic Order Form System

Frontend wajib menggunakan:

* code
* type
* billing_type

untuk menentukan:

* form order
* note order
* checkout flow

---

## Contoh

### Product Response

```json
{
  "code": "VT",
  "type": "esim",
  "billing_type": "monthly"
}
```

Frontend menentukan:

* form mana yang dirender
* field mana yang muncul
* note mana yang tampil

---

# Important Business Logic

## VT Product

Pembayaran bulanan:

* tanggal 20-28

---

## GJ Product

Pembayaran bulanan:

* tanggal 18-24

---

## E-SIM Product

Harus meminta:

* EID

---

## Phone + Internet Product

Harus meminta:

* eKYC

---

# Frontend Responsibilities

Frontend bertanggung jawab untuk:

## 1. Dynamic Form Rendering

Contoh:

```ts
if(product.code === 'VT')
```

render:

* VT Form

---

## 2. Dynamic Notes

Notes tidak disimpan di backend.

Frontend wajib menyediakan:

* note VT
* note GJ
* note E-SIM
* note Phone

---

## 3. WhatsApp Checkout Generator

Frontend wajib:

* collect form data
* generate WhatsApp text
* redirect ke WhatsApp

Backend tidak generate chat.

---

## 4. Theme System

Backend menyediakan setting theme.

Frontend wajib:

* membaca API theme
* apply warna/theme website

Theme concept:

* Spring
* Summer
* Autumn
* Winter

---

# Recommended Frontend Pages

## Homepage

Features:

* Hero banner
* Promo slider
* Best seller
* New products
* Categories

API:

```bash
/api/home
```

---

## Product List Page

Features:

* filter
* search
* category
* pagination (future)

API:

```bash
/api/products
```

---

## Product Detail Page

Features:

* product detail
* variants
* pricing
* dynamic form
* WhatsApp checkout

API:

```bash
/api/products/{slug}
```

---

## Search Component

Features:

* realtime search
* debounce

API:

```bash
/api/products?search=
```

---

# API Response Format

Semua API menggunakan:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Success",
  "data": []
}
```

Frontend wajib membaca:

* success
* message
* data

---

# Image System

Backend sudah otomatis:

* compress image
* convert webp
* resize image

Frontend tinggal gunakan URL image.

---

# Recommended Frontend Stack

Recommended:

* Next.js App Router
* Tailwind CSS
* Axios
* Zustand / Context API
* SwiperJS
* Framer Motion

---

# Important Notes

## Jangan hardcode product

Semua product wajib dari API.

---

## Jangan hardcode pricing

Semua pricing wajib dari API.

---

## Jangan hardcode variants

Semua variants wajib dari API.

---

## Form harus dynamic

Karena tiap product bisa beda flow.

---

# Suggested Frontend Architecture

```bash
src/
 ├── app/
 ├── components/
 ├── services/
 ├── hooks/
 ├── types/
 ├── lib/
 └── store/
```

---

# Recommended API Service Layer

Contoh:

```ts
services/product.ts
services/home.ts
services/promo.ts
```

